-- RBS Sees Total of 5,500 Job Losses from Restructuring
-- B y   J o n   M e n o n
-- 2012-01-12T07:05:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/rbs-sees-5-500-job-losses-from-restructuring.html
Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc (RBS) 
said it expects to cut 2,000 jobs in its investment banking unit
in the second half of 2011 and a further 3,500 over the next
three years.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
